name: iOS 15 AppStore Light & Dark
description:
Hi everyone !


This project provides you with a mockup of the App Store. This mockup is fully customizable, and you'll be able to see your app as in the App store. Simply change all the "Figma" references to any app of your choice and MAGIC !


This is my first Figma project, please let me know your thoughts and advices in the comments below !
